---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
import FooterCta from '../../components/FooterCta.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Anxiety & Depression — Arianna Buratti, Psychologist"
  description="Anxiety and depression therapy with Arianna Buratti in Carlton, Melbourne. Evidence-based treatment for anxiety, low mood, panic attacks, and emotional wellbeing."
  activeNav="services"
>

  <Hero
    title="Anxiety & Depression"
    subtitle="Evidence-based strategies for managing anxiety, low mood, and building emotional resilience."
    image="/images/service-anxiety.jpg"
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-section" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>You Don't Have to Face It Alone</h2>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p>Anxiety and depression are among the most common mental health concerns in Australia. They can affect every area of your life — your relationships, work, sleep, and sense of self. The good news is that effective treatments exist, and therapy can make a real difference.</p>
      <h3>Anxiety</h3>
      <p>Anxiety can show up as persistent worry, restlessness, physical tension, panic attacks, or avoidance of situations that feel overwhelming. I can help with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Generalised anxiety disorder (GAD)</li>
        <li>Panic attacks and panic disorder</li>
        <li>Social anxiety</li>
        <li>Health anxiety</li>
        <li>OCD and obsessive thinking</li>
        <li>Phobias</li>
        <li>Performance anxiety</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Depression</h3>
      <p>Depression often involves persistent low mood, loss of interest in things you used to enjoy, fatigue, difficulty concentrating, and feelings of worthlessness. I provide support for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Major depressive disorder</li>
        <li>Persistent low mood and sadness</li>
        <li>Loss of motivation and energy</li>
        <li>Bipolar disorder (mood management)</li>
        <li>Postnatal depression</li>
        <li>Seasonal changes in mood</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm">
    <div class="container content-section" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Treatment Approaches</h2>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p>I use a range of <a href="/approaches/">evidence-based approaches</a> to treat anxiety and depression, including Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT), Acceptance and Commitment Therapy (ACT), Mindfulness-Based Cognitive Therapy, and Interpersonal Therapy (IPT).</p>
      <p>Treatment is tailored to your specific symptoms, severity, and personal goals. We'll work together to understand what's driving your anxiety or depression, develop practical coping strategies, and build long-term emotional resilience.</p>
      <p>Sessions are available in person or via <a href="/telehealth/">telehealth</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FooterCta title="Ready to Start?" body="Reach out to book your first session or ask any questions." />

</BaseLayout>
